name: Get Out Of Earth
description:
This game defines art itself.

If your opinion is based, you get to live. If it's not, enjoy space dumdum.

WASD - Move 

Space - Yoink to space

You gain points when you throw away dumdums (indicated by the brain next to the icon)

You lose points if:

-You punch when no one is near you.

-You punch a smartie off the earth.

-Timer of a dumdum runs out before you punch them.
